race.description: Fair Dinkum Builds Cv Sheds 1-4 Win Ht 1 H
race.comment: FIERY PIASTRI (4) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when third (20.32) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Safe beginner who will go forward from trap three. Can turn form around here. TWO TONE TOMMY (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (28.88) in a Grade 5 at Casino. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. A big run wouldn't surprise. NEAT AND SWEET (7) doesn't win out of turn. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (24.05) at Casino. Expected to feature again. WOLFGANG (8) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.
